data.title: Dennis Quaid stars as Ronald Reagan in upcoming film
data.meta_description: Actor Dennis Quaid, who endorsed Donald Trump, joins 'Fox & Friends' to discuss the state of the Democratic Party after Biden's debate performance and preview his upcoming film, 'Reagan.'
